{"pageProps":{"blogPost":{"id":551,"title":"Top 5 Talent Acquisition Trends For 2022","content":"<p>As the year comes to an end, this week let’s take a look at the top 5 talent acquisition trends that defined 2021 and those that will pave the way for 2022.&nbsp;<br><br>1. Data-driven recruiting to grow in 2022 too! Data will be king and will define the way recruitment technologies are used.&nbsp;<br><br>2. AI-based recruitment tools to match the right candidate with the right job will improve and grow<br><br>3. Personalized nurturing will continue to provide a premier candidate experience<br><br>4. Diversity, Inclusion and equity will remain an acquisition priority<br><br>5. Employee referrals &amp; Internal mobility will be important aspects of acquiring the right talent.</p>","slug":"top-5-talent-acquisition-trends-for-2022","subTitle":"As the year comes to an end, this week let’s take a look at the top 5 talent acquisition trends that defined 2021 and those that will pave the way for 2022. ","sizeInGrid":null,"meta_description":null,"metaDesc":null,"published_at":"2021-12-28T12:17:49.028Z","created_at":"2021-12-28T12:17:45.101Z","updated_at":"2021-12-28T12:17:49.071Z","featuredImage":{"id":691,"name":"Top-5-Soft-Skills-Recruiters-Look-For.jpg","alternativeText":"","caption":"","width":1880,"height":1253,"formats":{"thumbnail":{"name":"thumbnail_Top-5-Soft-Skills-Recruiters-Look-For.jpg","hash":"thumbnail_Top_5_Soft_Skills_Recruiters_Look_For_3eaa6de4d2","ext":".jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":234,"height":156,"size":8.59,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/thumbnail_Top_5_Soft_Skills_Recruiters_Look_For_3eaa6de4d2.jpg"},"large":{"name":"large_Top-5-Soft-Skills-Recruiters-Look-For.jpg","hash":"large_Top_5_Soft_Skills_Recruiters_Look_For_3eaa6de4d2","ext":".jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":1000,"height":666,"size":81.36,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/large_Top_5_Soft_Skills_Recruiters_Look_For_3eaa6de4d2.jpg"},"medium":{"name":"medium_Top-5-Soft-Skills-Recruiters-Look-For.jp